            "type": "project",
            "additionalAssets": [
                "https://helpx.adobe.com/content/dam/help/en/premiere-pro/how-to/in-app/animate-your-titles/IMG_001.mp4"
            ],
            "minVersion": "15.0",
            "projectUrl": "https://helpx.adobe.com/content/dam/help/en/premiere-pro/how-to/in-app/animate-your-titles/Jillian-Nicole-Smith_TikTok1.prproj",
            "sizeBytes": "123456789",
            "steps": [
                {
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "autoplay": true,
                            "type": "video",
                            "videoUrl": "https://helpx.adobe.com/content/dam/help/en/premiere-pro/how-to/in-app/animate-your-titles/5b1d6fc9-65ce-4919-b4c1-adcecdd5db34.mp4"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Pick an eye-catching title",
                            "type": "heading"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Find a fun, free Motion Graphics template (mogrt) directly inside Premiere Pro and drop it onto your timeline. Then customize it and make it do cool things.",
                            "type": "text"
                        },
                        {
                            "listItems": [
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "isPanelOpen",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "panelName": "Graphics"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "Open the <$Essential Graphics$> panel by choosing <$Window$> > <$Essential Graphics$>."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "In the <$Browse$> tab of the <$Essential Graphics$> panel, click <$Adobe Stock$>."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Below the search box, check <$Free$> to limit search results to free templates."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Scroll through the selections. There's a lot! Hover over a thumbnail to see a preview of any animation provided by the template."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Type \"fast movement\" in the search box and press Enter or Return to narrow the results. I love the \"Fast Movement Response Promo Titles\" template."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "clipAdded",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Fast Movement Response Promo Titles",
                                                "layerName": "Video 2"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "Drag this template to the <$V2$> track in the <$Timeline$> panel so it's above the footage."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "ctiStopped"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "check": "ctiMoved"
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "showOnComplete": {
                                        "heading": "Right on!",
                                        "texts": [
                                            "You learned how to browse Adobe Stock for Motion Graphics templates in the <$Essential Graphics$> panel and add one to your sequence. In the next section, I show you how to customize it to suit your scene."
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "text": "Choose <$Sequence$> > <$Render In to Out$> to ensure smooth playback of the mogrt animation."
                                }
                            ],
                            "type": "listSubsteps"
                        },
                        {
                            "texts": [
                                "Adding a mogrt to a sequence automatically copies it to the <$Project$> panel within a new <$Motion Graphics Template Media$> folder."
                            ],
                            "type": "well",
                            "wellType": "info"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "autoplay": true,
                            "type": "video",
                            "videoUrl": "https://helpx.adobe.com/content/dam/help/en/premiere-pro/how-to/in-app/animate-your-titles/e1a32187-d5ef-40d1-aef1-607e1d7d1498.mp4"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Make it your own",
                            "type": "heading"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "It's easy to change up a Motion Graphics template the way you want. My example uses the free \"Fast Movement Response Promo Titles\" mogrt from Adobe Stock.",
                            "type": "text"
                        },
                        {
                            "listItems": [
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "isClipSelected",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Fast Movement Response Promo Titles"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "In the <$Timeline$> panel, select the mogrt you previously added to the sequence."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "In the <$Edit$> tab of the <$Essential Graphics$> panel, expand the <$Titles$> section and replace the Titles 1–3 placeholder entries with your own text. For Title 4, just enter a question mark: <$?$>"
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Click away to apply your edits to the template."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Expand the <$Style Controls$> section and turn off <$Background Color$>."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Expand the <$Global Controls$> section. For <$Global Position$>, set <$Y$> = <$750$>."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "ctiStopped"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "check": "ctiMoved"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "check": "ctiStopped"
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "showOnComplete": {
                                        "heading": "Success!",
                                        "texts": [
                                            "You learned how to customize a Motion Graphics template from Adobe Stock. In the next section, I show you how to animate the title in a fun way."
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "text": "Choose <$Sequence$> > <$Render In to Out$> to play the updated mogrt."
                                }
                            ],
                            "type": "listSubsteps"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "autoplay": true,
                            "type": "video",
                            "videoUrl": "https://helpx.adobe.com/content/dam/help/en/premiere-pro/how-to/in-app/animate-your-titles/efc70928-3cd6-4447-8f3e-bdc24c49944d.mp4"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Send it flying",
                            "type": "heading"
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Although a Motion Graphics template from Adobe Stock may come with prebuilt animations, the mogrt itself stays put. Let's make it appear to react to what's happening on screen.",
                            "type": "text"
                        },
                        {
                            "listItems": [
                                {
                                    "text": "Position the playhead where my hand appears to almost touch the question mark (about 9:06)."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "In the <$Timeline$> panel, select the mogrt."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "isPanelOpen",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "panelName": "Effect Controls"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "Open the <$Effect Controls$> panel by choosing <$Window$> > <$Effect Controls$>."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "keyframeAdded",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Fast Movement Response Promo Titles",
                                                "componentMatchName": "AE.ADBE Motion",
                                                "componentParameter": 0
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "In the <$Motion$> section of the <$Effect Controls$> panel, click the stopwatch next to <$Position$>. This tells Premiere Pro that you want to change that value over time — the basics of keyframe animation."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "ctiMoved"
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "In the <$Timeline$> panel, enter <$+4$> in the timecode indicator to advance the playhead four frames."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "keyframeAdded",
                                            "payload": {
                                                "clipName": "Fast Movement Response Promo Titles",
                                                "componentMatchName": "AE.ADBE Motion",
                                                "componentParameter": 0
                                            }
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "In the <$Effect Controls$> panel, adjust the values for <$Position$> so that <$X$> = <$1150$> and <$Y$> = <$1130$>, placing the question mark down and offscreen to the right."
                                },
                                {
                                    "checkUserInteractions": [
                                        {
                                            "check": "ctiStopped"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "check": "ctiMoved"
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "showOnComplete": {
                                        "heading": "Great!",
                                        "texts": [
                                            "You animated the position of a Motion Graphics template so it appears to interact with the action in the video."
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "text": "Play the sequence. The question mark animates between your recorded positions."
                                }
                            ],
                            "type": "listSubsteps"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "stepItems": [
                        {
                            "successHeading": "Nicely done!",
                            "successText": "Now that you've added a Motion Graphics template to your video, find more fun templates from Adobe Stock and explore ways to animate them creatively.",
                            "type": "endScreen"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
